title: Its About Time Episodes 21-26 DivX
description:
It's About Time

Here are the last six episodes of the series, where the cave people are dealing with life in the 20th century. (I wonder how they'd like the 21st?)

Episodes 21-26

# The Cave Family Swingers (aired: 2/5/1967)
# To Sign or Not to Sign (aired: 2/19/1967)
# School Days, School Days (aired: 2/26/1967)
# Our Brothers' Keepers (aired: 3/5/1967)
# The Stone Age Diplomats (aired: 3/12/1967)
# The Stowaway (aired: 4/2/1967)
